      "To obtain some independent verification of our tomographic estimates of the average temperature (and heat content) of the section, we can compare them with results from hydrographic cruises. In February 1994, a hydrographic survey was carried out which was designed to be nearly simultaneous and coincident with the acoustic section.",
      "The heat content (proportional to the averaged temperature) during the time of the cruise was found from the hydrographic data to be (7.21 \u00b1 0.16) x 10^21 J, whereas the tomographic value is (7.18 \u00b1 0.10) x 10^21 J."
