    "evidence_passages": [
      "The methods presented here were developed in the context of the GFDL Modular Ocean Model (MOM). As such, they are meant to be computationally efficient on a wide variety of parallel computing platforms.",
      "Nonetheless, the cost per step is trivial compared to the elliptic solve required by an implicit method, which generally requires global communication between processors on a parallel computer.",
