      "The analysis is based on a 50-year (1950\u20131999), eddy-permitting, global ocean data assimilation system from the ECCO (Estimating the Circulation and Climate of the Ocean) consortium. The system is based on the MIT general circulation model [Marshall et al., 1997a, 1997b] and its adjoint [Marotzke et al., 1999].",
