      "The parameterization of the eddy buoyancy flux proposed in this paper is rooted in the requirement that the total energy budget be satisfied.",
      "The parameterized eddy flux allows the conversion of available potential energy into eddy kinetic energy at a rate that balances the dissipation of eddy kinetic energy. The total energy budget is satisfied by construction."
