      "Fig. 9 shows the time series of the leading principal components of SST anomalies over the North Atlantic (top panel) and North Pacific (bottom panel), i.e., the North Atlantic Oscillation (NAO) and Pacific Decadal Oscillation (PDO) indices. The correlation with the corresponding observational indices are 0.61 and 0.49 respectively."
