    "evidence_passages": [
      "To test the hypothesis that the observed SSH rise is a direct result of wind forcing, we compare the SSH time series with the time integral of the Ekman pumping velocity, a simple model of the barotropic ocean response to wind forcing.",
      "Figure 3 shows the SSH anomaly averaged over the region 70.5\u201380.5\u25e6 N, 130\u2013170\u25e6 W (Fig. 1) compared with the time integral of the Ekman pumping velocity.",
