      "We applied two biogeochemical models, the Integrated Biosphere Simulator (IBiS) (Kucharik et al. 2000) and a modification of the Terrestrial Ecosystem Model (TEM) (McGuire et al. 2001). Both models used monthly climatic data at a spatial resolution of 0.5\u00b0 latitude by 0.5\u00b0 longitude for the historical period (Mitchell and Jones 2005) and for future scenarios (Nakicenovic et al. 2000).",
