    "justification": "The paper explicitly states that the models used for the large-scale analysis operate on a \"coarse spatial resolution,\" specifically mentioning static grids of 0.5\u00b0 x 0.5\u00b0 and 1\u00b0. Finer resolution data is aggregated up to these coarse model grids. This directly corresponds to the Level 1 criteria of \"Coarse: Low-resolution static grids\". There is no evidence of grid refinement or dynamic boundaries.",
