    "justification": "The paper directly compares a global metric (the trend in full-depth ocean heat content) from the CMIP5 model ensemble against new observational estimates. It provides specific quantitative values and confidence intervals for both the model and observational trends, demonstrating a statistical comparison of a global metric. This goes beyond a simple qualitative agreement (Level 1) and fits the criteria for a Level 2 statistical validation using a global bias/trend metric.",
