      "To examine whether the model can reproduce this bimodal variability, we calculated the probability density function (PDF) of the KE index, which is defined as the zonal velocity averaged over the region 143\u00b0\u2013150\u00b0 E, 34\u00b0\u201336\u00b0 N at 100 m depth (Qiu and Chen 2005). Figure 2 shows the PDF of the KE index from the AVISO data and the model simulation. Both the observation and the model simulation show a clear bimodal distribution, indicating that the model is able to reproduce the two preferred states of the KE system.",
