    "justification": "The paper performs a process-level validation of the model against independent satellite altimeter data (AVISO). The authors specifically test the model's ability to reproduce a key physical process: the bimodal variability of the Kuroshio Extension (KE). They do this by comparing statistical distributions (Probability Density Function) and temporal characteristics (power spectrum) of a KE index between the model and observations. This method of confirming that the model correctly simulates the dynamics of a specific, critical process against real-world data aligns with the criteria for Level 3.",
