    "justification": "The paper validates its model by comparing the modeled paleo-water depths against independent estimates derived from benthic foraminifera at several ODP sites. However, the assessment of this comparison is qualitative, using descriptive terms such as 'broadly consistent' and 'agrees well', and relies on visual inspection of plots. No quantitative statistical metrics (e.g., RMSE, bias) are provided to assess the model's goodness-of-fit. This subjective, 'eyeball' fit evaluation corresponds to Level 1.",
