      "The circulation is a steady-state annual mean derived from a time-evolving solution of the MITgcm that has been constrained by a variety of hydrographic and satellite data using the Green\u2019s function approach of Menemenlis et al.",
      "The transport operator A is constructed to be mass-conserving.",
