    "justification": "The paper analyzes the ECMWF 4D-Var system, which is described as an \"operational, state-of-the-art global data assimilation system\". This indicates a high level of maturity and maintenance. The mention that \"nonlinearities have increased over the years\" demonstrates a long history of development and continuous upgrades. Most importantly, the discussion of \"strategies for accommodating the increasing number of sequential outer loops in the tight schedules of operational global NWP\" is direct evidence of long-term strategic planning and roadmap development to ensure the system's future viability. This level of planning and operational maintenance is characteristic of Level 3 (Institutional).",
