      "The model is configured with a free surface and forced with a monthly climatology of wind stress, net heat and freshwater fluxes. The atmospheric forcing fields were derived from the Comprehensive Ocean\u2013Atmosphere Data Set (COADS) (Da Silva et al., 1994).",
