    "justification": "The paper describes a model that is \"forced\" by climatological datasets for its atmospheric surface conditions, initial state, and open boundary conditions. The model physics evolve based on these prescribed external data inputs. There is no mention of a system for assimilating observations into the model's interior state during the simulation (such as a Kalman Filter or 4D-Var). This approach, where the model is driven by data at its boundaries without a feedback mechanism to correct the internal state with observations, directly corresponds to the description of a Level 1 (Forced) system.",
