    "justification": "The paper validates its reconstructed historical sea-level record (the 'model') by comparing it against independent, real-world data. Specifically, the reconstructed monthly mean sea level is compared against instrumental records from other locations (New York City and Portland), and a quantitative statistical metric (R\u00b2) is reported. Furthermore, key parameters derived from the historical data (tidal constituents) are statistically compared to modern values, showing a quantitative difference (<1%). The use of global statistical metrics (R\u00b2, percentage difference) to assess the model's agreement with independent datasets directly meets the criteria for Level 2.",
