      "As the noise is assumed to be Gaussian, the least squares estimator is also Gaussian, with mean a(t) (since it is unbiased), and with a variance given by Var[\u00e2(t)] = \u03c3\u00b2(X(t)\u1d40X(t))\u207b\u00b9 (13)",
