      "The SSS data were obtained from the Aquarius level 3 monthly sea surface salinity standard mapped image data version 4.0... and from JAMSTEC gridded Argo data... We compared the two SSS data sets and confirmed that they have quite similar spatiotemporal features on the ENSO time scale, although the Argo-based SSS is slightly higher than the Aquarius SSS (Figure S1 in the supporting information).",
