      "The model used in this study is the Regional Oceanic Modeling System (ROMS)... a free-surface, hydrostatic, primitive equation ocean model.",
      "In our configuration, the third-order upstream biased advection scheme is used for both tracers and momentum (Shchepetkin and McWilliams, 2005).",
